data.description: Welcome to the enchanting Woodmill Pond community, where you'll discover a cluster of elegant twin-style homes, all without the encumbrance of HOA fees. Nestled within this serene neighborhood is a stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom abode, complete with a one-car garage, a partially fenced yard, and the convenience of off-street parking via both the garage and driveway.  As you step through the inviting front door, your feet will meet the luxurious LVP flooring that graces the entire open floorplan. Moving seamlessly from the living area to the kitchen and family room, you'll find a space that effortlessly flows into the backyard oasis. Here, a generously sized deck awaits, offering ample room for outdoor enjoyment and recreational activities.  Returning indoors, you'll be drawn to the cozy allure of a wood-burning fireplace, situated in a living space that also boasts a convenient half bathroom, a utility laundry room, and convenient garage access.  Venturing upstairs, you'll discover three spacious bedrooms, each designed with comfort and relaxation in mind. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom for added convenience, while an additional full bathroom is thoughtfully located in the hallway for easy access by all.   This captivating home awaits your visit. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours. Come experience it for yourself soon!
